<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We help people who are vulnerable because of their lack of mental capacity or young age to take advantage of the services offered by the justice system. This helps them to avoid being socially excluded. OSPT works with the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
